      ::
      $:  %c
      $%  ::  %writ: internal (intra-ship) file response
          ::
          $:  %writ
              ::  riot: response contents
              ::
              riot=riot:clay
          ==
          ::  %wris: response to %mult; many changed files
          ::
          $:  %wris
              ::  case: case of the new files
              ::
              ::    %wris can only return dates to us.
              ::
