      ::
      |^  ^-  build-receipt
          ::  load all marks.
          ::
          =^  load-marks-result  accessed-builds
            (load-marks-reachable-from [[%grow source] [%grab target] ~])
          ?:  ?=([%| *] load-marks-result)
            p.load-marks-result
